data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 3BR/2.5BA in sought-after Tomahawk. Nestled in 1.13 Acres, this home offers a private oasis w/ pool on cul-de-sac lot. Master bath & secondary baths have been updated.  Large kitchen w/ breakfast room overlooking the pool and koi ponds area. Family room w/ stone fireplace, wood flooring in dining & formal living room. Great basement area for kids or theater room with access to the backyard. All minutes away from great restaurants and shopping. Come visit the place you will soon call home. Voluntary HOA.   Seller is offering $10K in Closing Costs OR rate buy down credit!
